Package dfischer.proxysniffer

Core functions of the ZebraTester Proxy Recorder - Used by "Recorder Plug-Ins" and by the Proxy Recorder REST API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ProxyRecorderPluginInterface
    Interface for proxy recorder plug-ins.

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ProxyRecorderPluginIllegalArgumentException
    A runtime exception that can be thrown by recorder plug-ins in case if an illegal argument value is passed to the method manualCall(ProxyRecorderContext recorderContext, String[] arguments).
    ProxyRecorderPluginInternalErrorException
    A runtime exception that can be thrown by recorder plug-ins in case if an internal error occurs inside the plug-in.
    ProxyRecorderPluginManualCallNotAllowedException
    A runtime exception that indicates that manually calling a recorder plug-in is not allowed.
    ProxySnifferVarHandlerDupScopeException
    Duplicate var declaration with different scope.
    ProxySnifferVarHandlerInvNameException
    Invalid var name declaration - unsupported chars in var name.
    ProxySnifferVarHandlerKeywordException
    Invalid var name declaration - Java keyword.
